content.html: I’m having to rediscover myself as an ADHD’er. I’ve realized I got so far without a diagnosis because I inadvertently discovered how to trigger my hyperfocus almost at will… this helps me pass as “gifted” while in hyperfocus mode 1/4 #adhd
